<p>Thanks bower!</p>
<h2 id="including-the-font-awesome-css">Including the font-awesome.css <a class="headerlink" href="publishing-fonts#including-the-font-awesome-css" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Our first job is to get that <code>font-awesome.css</code> into our site. We know how
to do that - just add it to our <code>main.css</code> file. I'll copy the bootstrap
line then update it to <code>font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css</code>. Done.</p>
