<p>Great news! You already know how to copy files in Gulp! Just create the normal
pipe chain, but without any filters in the middle: <code>gulp.src(srcFiles)</code>,
then pipe that directly to <code>gulp.dest(outputDir)</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="42d1827ef8">
