	                                <p>The copy function doesn't work with folders.<br>I'm using flag icon and this wsn't working.</p><p>  app.copy(config.bowerDir+'/flag-icon-css/flags/*', config.assetDir+'/flags');</p><p>I had to use</p><p>  app.copy(config.bowerDir+'/flag-icon-css/flags/1x1/*', config.assetDir+'/flags/1x1');<br>    app.copy(config.bowerDir+'/flag-icon-css/flags/4x3/*', config.assetDir+'/flags/4x3');</p><p>It's ok in this case as there is only 2 folders.<br>just to mention.</p>
